OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMostly
OL,6,Fcloudy this evening with the odd spot
OL,7,Fof rain possible, some areas may see
OL,8,Fthe odd brighter spell. Cloud
OL,9,Fthickening overnight with more
OL,10,Fpersistent and heavy rain likely,
OL,11,Fparticularly in northern parts. Rather
OL,12,Fbreezy especially along coasts. Mild.
OL,13,
OL,14,CThursday:FRain lingering in the
OL,15,Fmorning, often heavy across northern
OL,16,Fparts of the region, but gradually
OL,17,Feasing through the day. Turning drier
OL,18,Fand brighter further south. Winds
OL,19,Feasing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
