OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FVery
OL,6,Fwarm over the Bank Holiday weekend
OL,7,Fwith plenty of sunshine and light
OL,8,Fwinds. Any early morning cloud near
OL,9,Fcoasts should burn back through the
OL,10,Fmorning each day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
